per Hugo Lloris.\n\nFrance had the better of the chances before the break \u2013 Rui Patricio saved smartly from Martial on two occasions, while Kingsley Coman looked sharp for the world champions.\n\nIt was rewarded in the 53rd minute when Adrien Rabiot\u2019s shot was parried by Rui Patricio straight into the path of Kante, who poked it in from two yards out.\n\nThe result means France goes top of group A3 with one game remaining, while Sweden\u2019s 2-1 win over Croatia in Saturday\u2019s other match means there remains a battle to avoid relegation.\n\n(With inputs from Agencies)","title":"Kante scores to send France into finals - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/15/142168/","video":[]}
